<p>Application Lifecycle Service is a polyglot Platform-as-a-Service (PaaS). You can easily
deploy applications written in a wide range of languages and web
frameworks using a variety of data services simply by pushing your
source code to the system.</p>
<p>Application Lifecycle Service handles the automatic configuration of the language runtime,
web server, application dependencies, databases, and other services.</p>
